snippet.title: Celebrities' Spirit Animals - Dave Grohl, Kanye West, Amber Heard, + More
snippet.description:
If you're new, Subscribe! → http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=94.3MAXfm

Northern Colorado psychic Marla Mitchell asks her spirit guides what spirit animals are with various celebrities and political figures, including Donald Trump, Johnny Depp, Justin Bieber, Hillary Clinton, Bernie Sanders, Paul McCartney, and more.

Hear Marla live every Wednesday at 8 a.m. MT with Mollie Kendrick on 94.3 The X and thexfrontrange.com!
